query:
SELECT 
  (SELECT id FROM students WHERE registrationNumber = '2024001') as studentId,
  lm.subjectId,
  lm.userId as professorId,
  s.name as subjectName
FROM learning_modules lm
INNER JOIN subjects s ON lm.subjectId = s.id
GROUP BY lm.subjectId, lm.userId, s.name
LIMIT 1;
